ut we should leave now." Everyone packed up I grew to a huge dragon everyone was able to get on including the vampire's they where light...I shrunk the barrior to protect everyone I even grabbed the horses I flew out of the temple...At first some of the vampires kinda braced themselves but I chuckled. (Hold on tight!) The barrior fluxes...I flew the whole and glided on the wind when it picked up. Almost out of the danger zone...I could see the edge of the forest. (How are you holding up Rose?) (I'm okay hehe I can keep going.) (Okay but don't push yourself once it hits night time take a break alright?) I nodded. We broke out of the tree's and headed onwards. phew that was tuff... Mary rubbed my scales. "Good job my little fire breather." I purred.The sun started to go down after hours of flying. (King)"Rose take us down."I nodded and descended. I gently let the horses down than everyone else.My sister's got on the horses with the knight's as I turned back I was esxousted...The king's brother wrapped me up in a cloak and carried me. I slept soundly the whole way. The man noticed two small horns pokeing out. I woke up when ever they stopped to rest and eat, The king's brother would hunt for me since I was still tireds. I heard them talking about traveling... I yawned and changed into a small dragon to spread my wing's.  I roared and sore high into the clouds, The king's brother would fallow closely. I had them all in a barrior. "You sure love to fly." "Ya I really do." I landed on his shoulder. "I do but I love the night better...maybe I'll show you why hehe. I'm ready to rejoin the other's... Thanks." He looked at me and smiled but only for a split second than he went back down. "Imma go on ahead..." I took off. Mary picked me up when I was far away... (Mary)"Why must you be alone?" "You know why...night is near..." " Come on no one will say anything... please." I sighed... I jumped down I told her to put some distance. My body started to grow as the shadow's envelop