"Than I would like to make a pack with you. Do you accept?" "Yes. What will you trade?" "My blood and a promise. I promise to protect you and be with you for enternity." "I accept in return I Also make a promise I will protect my new Master and everything he holds dear for enternity." "I accept." "The pack has been made complete... By my power's may we bond forever more..."  I changed back to human form as a magic circle surround both me and Sebastian. My horns and tail and wing's still showed and my scales where blend of black and red. Mary hugged me tight. (Mary)" I'm sorry...I'm so sorry..." I hugged her back. Than she noticed a new mark. "You made a new pack?" I nodded. (Sebastian)" Well that went well." (King)" So what happened?" "I made a pack with Rose...Forgive me brother it was the only way to save her and us." (King)" As long as you own up to it that's all I could ask. Now shay'll we head home Your sister's are all worried." I nodded but my body was still really weak... Sebastian cuaght me and picked me up. The king also picked up Mary she to was still weak from turning and we headed back to his kingdom where everyone waited. 
